      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, distinguished by its individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented rod bearing and throttle actuator service already completed. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, supported by an Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system and a precision-calibrated M Variable Differential Lock. Every panel maintains its original paint depth, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation, reflecting its sheltered history. This is a definitive example of naturally aspirated M-division engineering, preserved in its most pristine form.",
